8.金钱定义成功


Some people believe that success is best measured by how much money a person earns.
Others argue that money is not the most important factor in defining success.
Discuss both views and give your own opinion.

While financial achievement is considered a sign of success by some people,
others believe that factors such as happiness, contribution to society, and personal fulfillment are more important.
Discuss both views and give your opinion.


Social status 

beyond material wealth

multifaceted concept

In modern society, success is often associated with financial achievement.
While some people believe that a person’s income is the best indicator of success, others argue that money alone cannot fully define it.

Many people equate success with wealth, believing that a high income reflects personal achievement.

This essay will discuss both sides of the argument and explain why I believe success should be defined in a broader sense.




Success 
