	❌ Therefore, if to describe a person as success…
	✅ Therefore, to describe a person as successful…

	 yet remain unsuccessful in their personal relationships.


Success is a broad concept that can be interpreted in different ways.

Some people may achieve success in terms of financial wealth, yet remain unsuccessful in their personal relationships.

Others may succeed in both their careers and relationships, but still feel unhappy due to poor physical health.

Therefore, when describing a person as truly successful in a general sense, I believe happiness should be the top priority.
In addition, a successful person should also have the ability to bring happiness to others.